## 5. User Flows

### 5.1 Creating a New Client

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Dashboard] --> B[Click New Client]
    B --> C{Select Client Type}
    C -->|Politician| D[Politician Form]
    C -->|Corporate| E[Corporate Form]
    D --> F[Fill Basic Info]
    E --> F
    F --> G[Add Contact Details]
    G --> H[Assign Department]
    H --> I[Set Account Manager]
    I --> J[Add Initial Guidelines]
    J --> K[Save Client]
    K --> L[Redirect to Client Detail]
```

### 5.2 Client Search and Filter

1. **Quick Search**: Instant search across name, tags, notes
2. **Advanced Filters**: 
   - Client type (politician/corporate)
   - Status (active/inactive/prospect)
   - Department assignment
   - Tags
   - Date ranges
3. **Saved Filters**: Users can save filter combinations
4. **Export**: Filtered results can be exported (CSV/PDF)

### 5.3 Managing Client Guidelines

```typescript
// Guidelines management flow
interface GuidelineFlow {
  steps: [
    'Select guideline type (Do/Don\'t)',
    'Choose category',
    'Write guideline text',
    'Set priority level',
    'Save with audit trail'
  ];
  validation: {
    maxLength: 500;
    requiresCategory: true;
    allowedCategories: ['communication', 'topics', 'branding', 'events'];
  };
}
```

