## 7. Search Implementation

### 7.1 Full-Text Search

```typescript
// Using PostgreSQL full-text search
interface SearchImplementation {
  // Indexed fields with weights
  fields: {
    name: 'A',        // Highest weight
    displayName: 'B',
    tags: 'C',
    notes: 'D'        // Lowest weight
  };
  
  // Search features
  features: [
    'Fuzzy matching',
    'Prefix search',
    'Tag filtering',
    'Type-ahead suggestions',
    'Search history'
  ];
}
