## 9. Security & Permissions

### 9.1 Access Control Matrix

| Feature | Admin | User (Same Dept) | User (Other Dept) | Account Manager |
|---------|-------|------------------|-------------------|-----------------|
| View Client List | All | Department Only | No | Assigned Only |
| View Client Details | All | Department Only | No | Assigned Only |
| Create Client | Yes | No | No | No |
| Edit Client | Yes | No | No | Assigned Only |
| Delete Client | Yes | No | No | No |
| Manage Guidelines | Yes | View Only | No | Yes |
| Upload Documents | Yes | Yes | No | Yes |
| View Activity | Yes | Yes | No | Yes |

### 9.2 Data Validation

```typescript
// Using Zod for validation (industry standard)
import { z } from 'zod';

const clientSchema = z.object({
  name: z.string().min(2).max(255),
  client_type: z.enum(['politician', 'corporate', 'ngo', 'government_body']),
  primary_email: z.string().email().optional(),
  primary_phone: z.string().regex(/^\+?[\d\s-()]+$/).optional(),
  tags: z.array(z.string()).max(10),
});
```

